import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import{ FormGroup, FormControl,Validators} from '@angular/forms' import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-login', templateUrl: './login.component.html', styleUrls: ['./login.component.css'] }) export class LoginComponent { login = new FormGroup({ email: new FormControl('',[Validators.required,Validators.email]), password: new FormControl('', [Validators.required,Validators.minLength(4),Validators.maxLength(6)]) }) constructor(private router:Router){} submit(){ console.log("Login Sucessful",this.login.value ) this.router.navigateByUrl('patient/home') } }
